<BaseLayout title="The Complete Guide to Lawn Irrigation in Indiana" description="Everything central Indiana homeowners need to know about sprinkler systems: types, costs, installation process, seasonal maintenance, and water savings tips.">
  <Hero
    title="The Complete Guide to Lawn Irrigation in Indiana"
