          <p class="text-gray-600">Your system sleeps while we handle <a href="/services/snow-removal" class="text-green-mid hover:text-green-dark underline">snow removal</a> to keep your property safe.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-2xl text-green-dark mt-12 mb-4">How Much Does an Irrigation System Cost?</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg mb-6">Costs vary based on property size, number of zones, and complexity. For a typical central Indiana residential property, you can expect to invest between $3,000 and $6,000 for a professionally installed system using commercial-grade components.</p>
