      <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg mb-6">Whether you're building a new home or want to upgrade an existing property, a professional irrigation system is one of the best investments you can make in your outdoor space. <a href="/contact" class="text-green-mid hover:text-green-dark underline">Contact Allen Irrigation</a> today for a free consultation.</p>
